  "body": "Steps to reproduce:\r\n\r\npaste\r\n```\r\nvar filter = web3.eth.filter('latest');\r\nfilter.watch(function (error, log) {\r\n    if(!error) {\r\n        status.sendMessage(log.toString()); \r\n    } else {\r\n        status.sendMessage(error.toString());\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n```\r\ninto a js file and add as a chat bot\r\n\r\nreturns a message with:\r\n\r\nError: EOF",
