    "body": "As I understand filters are relying on subscriptions https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/RPC-PUB-SUB and we don't support them in our transport layer at the moment. In order to support them, we need to switch transport to unix sockets or web sockets or implement subscriptions using signals.\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/6250754?s=400&v=4\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"https://assets-cdn.github.com/favicon.ico\" height=\"14\"> GitHub</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum\">ethereum/go-ethereum</a></strong></div><div>go-ethereum - Official Go implementation of the Ethereum protocol</div></blockquote>",
